            "Here are some key points about Machine Learning:\n",
            "\n",
            "1. Types: There are three main types of Machine Learning:\n",
            "   - Supervised Learning: The system learns from labeled training data.\n",
            "   - Unsupervised Learning: The system discovers hidden structures in the data.\n",
            "   - Reinforcement Learning: The system learns by interacting with an environment and receiving feedback through rewards and penalties.\n",
            "\n",
            "2. Applications: Machine Learning is used in various fields such as computer vision, natural language processing, speech recognition, recommendation systems, fraud detection, and more.\n",
            "\n",
            "3. Key concepts:\n",
            "   - Model Training: The algorithm learns from the provided data.\n",
            "   - Evaluation Metrics: Accuracy, precision, recall, F1 score, etc., measure how well the model performs.\n",
            "   - Overfitting vs. Underfitting: Overfitting occurs when the model is too complex and captures noise; underfitting occurs when it's too simple and fails to capture important features.\n",
            "\n",
            "4. Challenges: Handling large datasets efficiently, dealing with missing values, managing computational resources, ensuring fairness and transparency in decision-making\n",
            "You: Who created Python language?\n",
            "Chatbot: Python was created by Guido van Rossum in 1989 while he was a researcher at CWI (Centrum Wiskunde & Informatica) in Amsterdam, the Netherlands. Guido van Rossum has been the principal author and active leader of the development of the Python programming language since its creation. He left CWI in 1995 but continued working on Python full-time until 2000. Since then, he has remained a major contributor to the project.\n",
            "You: Thank you very much \n",
            "Chatbot: You're welcome! If you have any other questions, feel free to ask.\n",
            "You: quit\n",
            "Chatbot: Goodbye!\n"
